{"tid":1555651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有藍嘅父母真係好辛苦","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:37:48.000Z","uid":156419,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8d8c3b977ed3f641c1e23263d3cacb73ce4ad1","tid":1555651,"uid":156419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"啱啱食飯聽到老母屌示威者，重要屌咗好耐，跟住我就忍唔住同佢理論，俾曬啲片同相佢睇話班黑警先至係罪魁禍首，佢就乜都扮睇唔到，話你哋班後生仔中晒毒，俾人洗曬腦，叫佢俾啲證據嚟睇吓示威者點衰法，淨係識話有晒片啦但又攞唔出，又係淨係識講破壞經濟同埋犯法，跟住我就話我都有出去發夢順便叫佢都應該落下去現場睇下，唔好淨係識可匿埋係屋企講嘢，佢就再屌多兩錢重，最後我都費事嘈，講咗句「唔想同冇良心嘅人講野」就返房，依家個心好唔舒服，有啲想喊，點解啲人可以咁冇良心，仲要係我父母，好想離開呢個屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00cda1e938d295f64be318e4060f4b500c1bdac","tid":1555651,"uid":156188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"好明白，加油"},{"pid":"0a6be9745d06deedf2833027183356e94fba7e71","tid":1555651,"uid":3079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nU are not alone"},{"pid":"610d8344946fc945614eb26dd0a7740e651eb140","tid":1555651,"uid":156419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"真係好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7b42e1c86e59c54a1f6d25db725673bdf6f1d5","tid":1555651,"uid":33898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"自從31/8開始冇同屋企講過野 當佢地死咗算"},{"pid":"f045dd914b9abf799a4688d83ce7af947b50f24c","tid":1555651,"uid":247557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"有咩上黎一齊傾<br />\n忍到有能力就搬出去住"},{"pid":"a5e702ba42f91360797282146c40c3697cdb4c96","tid":1555651,"uid":156419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da7b42e1c86e59c54a1f6d25db725673bdf6f1d5","tid":1555651,"uid":33898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"自從31/